{"tid":1179050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普：對所有墨西哥商品征收5%的關稅","createTime":"2019-05-31T00:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T04:25:50.000Z","uid":252013,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f88a3888a2b0a5f0186aa6f6a98c82d65812e1b8","tid":1179050,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:03:24.000Z","msg":"我係墨西哥應該會心諗，同你簽黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nUSMCA都未生效又玩過.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年5月31日<br />\n07:31 特朗普：6月10日起對進口自墨西哥的所有商品征收5%的關稅；關稅會逐步上調，直至非法移民問題得到解決，屆時會結束征收關稅。<br />\n<br />\n來自秒聞 ‧ 實時財經急報app<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mutemute.com/share.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mutemute.com%2Fshare.php&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=c0db34c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mutemute.com/share.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年5月18日<br />\n中美貿易戰仍然膠着之際，美國總統特朗普周五（17日）宣布，已跟加拿大和墨西哥達成協議，將會取消向兩國徵收鋼鋁關稅，而加墨兩國亦會取消向美國產品徵收的報復性商品關稅。加拿大總理杜魯多指，美國取消關稅後，對新的北美自貿協議獲通過感到樂觀。 <br />\n<br />\n根據美加的聯合聲明中，兩國同意將於48小時內取消相關關稅。而美國和墨西哥亦達成相同協議。加墨兩國將取消對美國豬肉、威士忌和橙汁的關稅，美國的農戶和商界對政府跟加墨兩國達成協議感高興。美國副總統彭斯稱本月30日會到加拿大跟該國總理杜魯多見面，促進美墨加協定（USMCA）盡快落實。 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普去年宣布向中國、加拿大等多國徵收鋼鋁關稅。美國貿易代表萊蒂澤與加拿大外長方慧蘭，周三（15日）在美國首都華盛頓舉行會議，討論鋼鋁關稅與美墨加協定。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190518/mobile/bkn-20190518020112864-0518_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190518%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190518020112864-0518_00972_001.html&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=7bd9f609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190518/mobile/bkn-20190518020112864-0518_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bd200f1020ddc3863153a629411f3e9683bbdf48","tid":1179050,"uid":52215,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:04:09.000Z","msg":"傻閪侵以為自己好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a24148ecce9b1005f8ffe5e09cc3ff6b08d0fde","tid":1179050,"uid":59546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:05:59.000Z","msg":"美帝呢招打殘中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有咩國頂得順呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 墨西哥呢d細國想玩都冇得玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed812ec4081afc158a6b2da28961baf7a8f66af","tid":1179050,"uid":59546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:06:48.000Z","msg":"就算對全球加關稅都吹美帝唔脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06bc84f3b0a9326e8afd20197175724e03fd3a4a","tid":1179050,"uid":252013,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a24148ecce9b1005f8ffe5e09cc3ff6b08d0fde","tid":1179050,"uid":59546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:05:59.000Z","msg":"美帝呢招打殘中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲有咩國頂得順呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 墨西哥呢d細國想玩都冇得玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:19:05.000Z","msg":"個個都玩..."},{"pid":"44cd7f761ca95c6bcde8f5acb26d21277ee6a79c","tid":1179050,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd200f1020ddc3863153a629411f3e9683bbdf48","tid":1179050,"uid":52215,"like":8,"dislike":10,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:04:09.000Z","msg":"傻閪侵以為自己好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T00:20:40.000Z","msg":"又一隻三毛狗?"},{"pid":"695c2174a1ba634912c3600baced56ae6116393d","tid":1179050,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ed812ec4081afc158a6b2da28961b